[h3 id=GadgetsUsed 
	" Gadgets used
	$LF
]h3
[h4 id=BlueCopter 
	" Blue copter
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"The blue copter is obviously used to move faster than walking. It is only useful over long distances because its duration is timed. However, I had more hats in this run so I could use it even for short distances. When the blue copter symbol is flashing, Gadget will be invincible while using it.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=RedCopter 
	" Red copter
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"A damaging copter that can be controlled. It is the main weapon used for fighting bosses because of its strength and its ability to be controlled. I didn't use one on level 3's boss this time because he can be killed with just punches, so I have no need to waste the hats.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=HookGrappleThing 
